NOTE: For best performance, we recommend a version like 1.12.2 + Optifine or the latest Minecraft with Sodium/Lithium/Phosphor Fabric Mods.

Minecraft Java MultiMC5 for the raspberry pi
To run: Menu -> Games -> MultiMC
To run in a terminal: ~/MultiMC/install/MultiMC

the MultiMC5 install script contains OS detection (ubuntu and debian based systems supported), and automatic java 8, 11, and 16 download and installation

MultiMC5 supports mojang and microsoft account login support, and minecraft versions from the old beta/alphas all the way up to 1.17+. Fabric and Forge mod loading is supported for the applicable minecraft versions

A custom meta repo is used for arm32 and arm64 to provide lwjgl 2.9.4, 3.1.6, 3.2.1, and 3.2.2 native libraries